{"snp5.15:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.15 ","snp5.15:0.2":"Posalamanavapuccha ","snp5.15:1.1":"“Yo atitam adisati, ","snp5.15:1.2":"(iccayasma posalo) ","snp5.15:1.3":"Anejo chinnasamsayo; ","snp5.15:1.4":"Paragum sabbadhammanam, ","snp5.15:1.5":"Atthi panhena agamam. ","snp5.15:2.1":"Vibhutarupasannissa, ","snp5.15:2.2":"sabbakayappahayino; ","snp5.15:2.3":"Ajjhattanca bahiddha ca, ","snp5.15:2.4":"natthi kinciti passato; ","snp5.15:2.5":"Nanam sakkanupucchami, ","snp5.15:2.6":"katham neyyo tathavidho”. ","snp5.15:3.1":"“Vinnanatthitiyo sabba, ","snp5.15:3.2":"(posalati bhagava) ","snp5.15:3.3":"Abhijanam tathagato; ","snp5.15:3.4":"Titthantamenam janati, ","snp5.15:3.5":"Vimuttam tapparayanam. ","snp5.15:4.1":"Akincannasambhavam natva, ","snp5.15:4.2":"Nandi samyojanam iti; ","snp5.15:4.3":"Evametam abhinnaya, ","snp5.15:4.4":"Tato tattha vipassati; ","snp5.15:4.5":"Etam nanam tatham tassa, ","snp5.15:4.6":"Brahmanassa vusimato”ti. ","snp5.15:4.7":"Posalamanavapuccha cuddasama. "}